<p>Let's say I have <code>error_reporting</code> set to <code>E_ALL &amp; ~E_STRICT</code> and an error of level <code>E_USER_NOTICE</code> (or any other level) is triggered. </p>  <p>How can I check if that <code>E_USER_NOTICE</code> matches or doesn't match the above <code>E_ALL &amp; ~E_STRICT</code>?</p>  <p>To clarify, given the example above, <strong>if</strong> <code>error_reporting(E_ALL &amp; ~E_STRICT)</code> equaled an array of <code>[E_ERROR, E_NOTICE, E_WARNING ...]</code>, how could I check if <code>E_NOTICE</code> was in that metaphorical array.</p>